#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.78"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.78:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.78:0.2"
msgid "8. Ānandavagga "
msgstr "8. Ānanda "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.78:0.3"
msgid "78. Sīlabbatasutta "
msgstr "78. Precepts and Observances "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.225, sc1
msgctxt "an3.78:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

msgctxt "an3.78:1.2"
msgid "“sabbaṃ nu kho, ānanda, sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ saphalan”ti? "
msgstr "“Ānanda, are all precepts and observances, lifestyles, and spiritual paths fruitful when taken as the essence?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.78:1.3"
msgid "“Na khvettha, bhante, ekaṃsenā”ti. "
msgstr "“This is no simple matter, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.78:1.4"
msgid "“Tena hānanda, vibhajassū”ti. "
msgstr "“Well then, Ānanda, break it down.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: Yañhissa → yathārūpaṃ hissa (?)
msgctxt "an3.78:2.1"
msgid "“Yañhissa, bhante, sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ sevato akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti kusalā dhammā parihāyanti, evarūpaṃ sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ aphalaṃ. "
msgstr "“Take the case of someone who cultivates precepts and observances, a lifestyle, and a spiritual path, taking this as the essence. If unskillful qualities grow while skillful qualities decline, that’s not fruitful. "

#. VAR: Yañca khvāssa → yañca khvassa (s1-3) | yañhissa (mr) | yathārūpañca khvāssa (?)
msgctxt "an3.78:2.2"
msgid "Yañca khvāssa, bhante, sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ sevato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti, kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti, evarūpaṃ sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ saphalan”ti. "
msgstr "However, if unskillful qualities decline while skillful qualities grow, that is fruitful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.78:2.3"
msgid "Idamavoca āyasmā ānando. "
msgstr "That’s what Ānanda said, "

msgctxt "an3.78:2.4"
msgid "Samanuñño satthā ahosi. "
msgstr "and the teacher approved. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.78:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando “samanuñño me satthā”ti, uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
msgstr "Then Ānanda, knowing that the teacher approved, got up from his seat, bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before leaving. "

msgctxt "an3.78:3.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā acirapakkante āyasmante ānande bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then, not long after Ānanda had left, the Buddha addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "an3.78:3.3"
msgid "“sekho, bhikkhave, ānando; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, Ānanda is a trainee, "

msgctxt "an3.78:3.4"
msgid "na ca panassa sulabharūpo samasamo paññāyā”ti. "
msgstr "but it’s not easy to find his equal in wisdom.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.78:3.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
